{
  "stem": "18813.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 24.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was the one nominated to go down near the city to bring the-- so the Czech-- we went to Czechoslovakia, to-- because that was in Czechoslovakia-- and to, to Poland.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And wherever we stopped-- because we were still in the uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Nobody-- everybody could recognize us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we-- the bakeries, they said, please, wait another hour or something.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm putting a cake in the oven.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you will have it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So bread and cake, they give it to us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were asking, begging for that until we hit the Polish border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Polish border, we came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I never forget what they said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They said, Jesus, Maria, so many-- so many Jews arriving.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were five-- first ones, OK?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So you see, they didn't like the Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I went there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only one who knew my niece is, is my friend who lives in Montreal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because I said, if I don't survive, there's a little girl over there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You take out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when I came for my little niece, she said, somebody is looking for you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And only person who knew-- because I was scared-- was my friend.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew she was there already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we met.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Can you describe the-- what the reunion was like between you and your niece?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She was, at that time, maybe seven years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know if she was five because she was a little thing.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I took her.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a-- some people give me an apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she slept with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the one bed was for this guy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The other one was-- you know, we shared together.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had that apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
